<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/school-teachers-review-body> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The School Teachers’ Review Body (STRB) makes recommendations on the pay, professional duties and working time of school teachers in England and reports to the Secretary of State for Education and the Prime Minister. STRB is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Education ."@en .
